🔁 Real-Time Logging Hooks
In auth_routes.py, insert:

python
from app.utils.telemetry import log_identity_event
Use like this after login success:

python
log_identity_event("LOGIN_SUCCESS", user_id=user.id, email=user.email)
Or after failed MFA:

python
log_identity_event("MFA_FAIL", user_id=user_id, reason="Incorrect code", attempted_code=submitted_code)
These get pushed into Redis with TTL or persisted if configured.

